      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the draft. it's definitely got the right punch. i want to lean even harder into the part about the \"attacks\" on the family. can you add a section that gets more specific about why these progressive policies are actually dangerous for the next generation? like, make it clear that their version of \"progress\" is a direct threat to the survival of the traditional family unit.",
